deck: Spidey faces off against Turbo Jet.
description:
Citizens of New York are rallying against Spider-Man because of the presence of the Robin Hood-like character named Turbo Jet while residents of a local area are being threatened to move out of their homes. How can Spidey get out of this?

Note 1: Turbo Jet is primarily based on Rocket Racer.

Note 2: In the scene where Peter was in his room, Aunt May, Uncle Ben, Richard and Mary Parker appeared as photographs.

Sub-Note 2.5: Since neither Aunt May, Uncle Ben, Richard Parker nor Mary Parker appeared physically, they are not categorized as characters.
